I"<h2 id="需求">需求</h2>
<ul>
  <li>我想找个raspbian下的音乐播放器？用百度？</li>
  <li>我想找个冷门的工具？百度无解，怎么办？
基于多个我想……，我在开发中发现了以下本地查询包名称的方案。</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="查询包名称的命令">查询包名称的命令</h2>

<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>
<span class="nb">sudo </span>apt-cache search <span class="s2">"xxx"</span>

<span class="c"># 比如我想找个音频播放器</span>
<span class="nb">sudo </span>apt-cache search <span class="s2">"audio player"</span> 
得到关键词qmmp


<span class="nb">sudo </span>apt-cache search <span class="s2">"foobar"</span> 
<span class="c"># 得到关键信息lxmusic</span>


<span class="c"># 终端返回的信息量太大，怎么办？</span>
<span class="nb">cd</span> ~
<span class="nb">sudo </span>apt-cache search <span class="s2">"edit"</span> <span class="o">&gt;&gt;</span> 1.txt
<span class="c"># 然后查看1.txt文件</span>

<span class="c"># 显示更多用法：</span>
<span class="nb">sudo </span>apt-cache <span class="nt">--help</span>


</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="安装软件和卸载软件">安装软件和卸载软件</h2>
<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c"># 安装</span>
<span class="nb">sudo </span>apt-get <span class="nb">install </span>qmmp <span class="nt">-y</span>

<span class="c"># 卸载</span>
<span class="nb">sudo </span>apt-get autoremove qmmp

<span class="c"># 帮助</span>
<span class="nb">sudo </span>apt-get <span class="nt">--help</span>

</code></pre></div></div>

